00:32:22.670 --> 00:32:23.810
remember it.

00:32:23.810 --> 00:32:24.978
That's why we're here for.

00:32:24.978 --> 00:32:25.954
Film this.

00:32:25.954 --> 00:32:27.906
Bring it back to home.

00:32:27.906 --> 00:32:30.824
Show it to everybody, and show
