00:33:46.530 --> 00:33:49.640
One, for them to fall in love,
as everybody does that goes on

00:33:49.640 --> 00:33:50.870
these trips.

00:33:50.870 --> 00:33:53.420
But secondly, to see it from a
Chinese perspective and then

00:33:53.420 --> 00:33:54.470
to be able to articulate.

00:33:54.470 --> 00:33:57.100
So now, when Yao talks to
people-- and he's actually a

00:33:57.100 --> 00:33:58.880
National People's Congress
member now, as well.

00:33:58.880 --> 00:34:01.800
So he may even be moving
legislation on this forward,

00:34:01.800 --> 00:34:02.870
which is great.

00:34:02.870 --> 00:34:05.280
You know to speak from their
own personal experience.

00:34:05.280 --> 00:34:08.250
And you can't go out there and
see the stuff that we have to

00:34:08.250 --> 00:34:11.820
see without it moving you.

00:34:11.820 --> 00:34:13.580
And we hope that we can
bring this back.

00:34:13.580 --> 00:34:16.179
I think it's probably going to
be the first time you've had a

00:34:16.179 --> 00:34:19.389
