But are there any, I guess,
organizations that instead of

00:40:19.370 --> 00:40:21.860
having people, tourists, going
out on safaris, going out

00:40:21.860 --> 00:40:24.060
instead and trying to help
with organizations like

00:40:24.060 --> 00:40:26.040
WildAid or other non-profits.

00:40:26.040 --> 00:40:28.170
PETER KNIGHTS: There are some
