So Save the Elephants
you saw there.

00:40:46.200 --> 00:40:49.510
They have volunteers come and
help them work out there.

00:40:49.510 --> 00:40:50.130
And there's actually---

00:40:50.130 --> 00:40:51.130
DIANE SOLINGER: Strong partner
for you, correct?

00:40:51.130 --> 00:40:52.010
PETER KNIGHTS: Yeah, yeah.

