again is a great way of

00:41:09.440 --> 00:41:11.400
seeding back the message and
getting it back there.

00:41:11.400 --> 00:41:14.740
And I think increasingly what
we're seeing now is there's

00:41:14.740 --> 00:41:16.750
going to be tremendous
interest from China.

00:41:16.750 --> 00:41:19.250
There's tremendous economic
interest from China in Africa.

00:41:19.250 --> 00:41:21.180
