out and see a live
elephant, have an

00:41:29.930 --> 00:41:32.060
experience of a lifetime?

00:41:32.060 --> 00:41:34.850
Because part of the other thing
we want to do with this

00:41:34.850 --> 00:41:37.810
film is to explain to people
that you don't need to be

00:41:37.810 --> 00:41:39.090
scared of going to Africa.

