It's a pretty safe place.

00:41:40.250 --> 00:41:42.110
And you're not going to come
down with dengue fever the

00:41:42.110 --> 00:41:43.910
first day you arrive and
things like that.

00:41:43.910 --> 00:41:46.480
And so to encourage more and
more people from China to go

00:41:46.480 --> 00:41:49.260
to Africa and see
for themselves.

00:41:49.260 --> 00:41:53.300
DIANE SOLINGER: And Google has
