in trying to help people with
their economic prosperity and

00:41:56.990 --> 00:41:58.770
be entrepreneurs and put their
businesses online.

00:41:58.770 --> 00:42:04.100
And as we do that in our role,
we just kind of wonder how do

00:42:04.100 --> 00:42:08.020
we do that and help people in a
