00:42:08.020 --> 00:42:11.020
way as they become new consumers
and build those

00:42:11.020 --> 00:42:14.740
economic kind of prosperities
in their countries, making

00:42:14.740 --> 00:42:17.500
sure that this is part of
the conscience somehow.

00:42:17.500 --> 00:42:17.740
It's something maybe
we can do.

00:42:17.740 --> 00:42:18.770
PETER KNIGHTS: It's all
about awareness.

